Global Cash Automation (Management) Market Insights
Cash Automation (Management) Market size was valued at USD 8.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 14.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Cash Automation (Management) Market Overview
The global Cash Automation (Management) market was valued at approximately USD 22 billion in 2023, and it is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 10% over the forecast period from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing adoption of automated solutions in sectors such as banking, retail, and hospitality. Cash automation technologies are designed to optimize cash handling and management processes, ensuring security, efficiency, and cost-effectiveness. Automated Teller Machines (ATMs), cash recyclers, cash sorting machines, and point-of-sale (POS) systems are some of the key solutions driving this market forward.

